title: Chelsea Clinton slams Trump over North Korea response
text: 'How many of Mar-a-Lago's new members are foreign intelligence?': Chelsea Clinton slams Trump for formulating response to the North Korea missile test during a swanky dinner and under cell phone lights President Donald Trump hosted Japanese Prime Minister Shinzo Abe at his Mar-a-Lago estate in Florida this weekend On Saturday, Trump faced potentially his first international crisis when it was learned that North Korea test-launched a ballistic missile Trump and his aides scrambled to respond to the missile test in the middle of dinner at Mar-a-Lago Chelsea Clinton criticized the haphazard manner in which a potential crisis was being handled
